<h2><b>Is UpdraftPlus Premium worth it?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For all the additional benefits and perks that it brings, we feel that UpdraftPlus Premium is more than worth it if you truly value the safety and security of your WordPress site. With Premium you can exercise full control over your backups by unlocking enhanced security features and free updates. From accessing the latest UpdraftPlus Add-Ons for a year, to free support via our forum and email for a year, extra remote storage options, incremental backups and free tokens for UpdraftClone.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">UpdraftPlus Premium is what total security and peace of mind looks like!¬†</span></p>
